  f (⨅ i, g i) = ⨅ i, f (g i) :=
@monotone.map_supr_of_continuous_at' αᵒᵈ βᵒᵈ _ _ _ _ _ _ ι _ f g Cf Mf.dual

/-- If a monotone function sending `top` to `top` is continuous at the indexed infimum over
